      <h1 id="ciphers_font">Ciphers</h1>
      <p>A cipher is the <span id="bold">algorithm</span> used for performing encryption or decryption.
      To encipher or encode is to convert information into cipher or code.</p>
      <p>When using a cipher the original information is known as plaintext, and the encrypted form as ciphertext. The ciphertext message contains
      all the information of the plaintext message, but is not in a format readable by a human or computer without the proper mechanism to decrypt it.</p>
